keeps.title: భగవద్గిత
keeps.info:
Gopala Krishna bhagavan ki jai
Geetha matha ki jai
Pavan sutha hanuman ki jai 
Mahalakshmi matha ki jai 
Edukondala vada venkataramana Govinda Govinda 
Lakshmi ramana Govinda Govinda
Rama ramana Govinda Govinda 
Sri Sri Sri Nithyashudhananda Giri swamulavariki jai
Om Sri krishna parabhrahmane namah
